administrative orders are warranted to address", "issues that have arisen with respect to implementation of the CTAA Measures.", "3. Issues or proposals related to fees or costs imposed on parties to court proceedings", "(\u201cAssessments\u201d) that were not addressed by the CTAA Measures, including but not limited to:", "a. Assessment waivers in traffic cases;", "b. Assessments in juvenile cases; and", "c. Elimination of Assessments in criminal cases involving a sentence in excess of a", "specified length.", "4. Recommendations pertaining to the reporting of data concerning the imposition, collection", "or waiver of Assessments.", "Interested individuals may register to provide oral testimony at the public hearing by contacting", "Hayley Yussman at hyussman@illinoiscourts.gov no later than Tuesday, July 6, 2021. A Zoom", "link will be provided via email prior to the public hearing date. Registered speakers will be allotted", "10 minutes to address the Task Force.", "Members of the public will be able to view the hearing online at the Illinois Supreme Court\u2019s", "YouTube page at https://www.youtube.com/c/illinoiscourts.", "Written comments may also be submitted no later than Tuesday, July 6, 2021, via email to Hayley", "Yussman at hyussman@illinoiscourts.gov.", "Clerks of Court are requested to post a copy of this notice in a conspicuous place.", "For more information about the Supreme Court Statutory Court Fees Task Force, see the", "administrative order creating the Task Force and the related press release on the Supreme Court\u2019s website."], "bbox": [[0.374412, 0.119259, 0.251106, 0.020974], [0.506569, 0.149701, 0.06427499999999986, 0.014682], [0.254216, 0.141263, 0.49160000000000004, 0.025169], [0.666667, 0.17851, 0.2156459999999999, 0.012584], [0.112843, 0.18115, 0.10578599999999999, 0.014011], [0.768034, 0.191612, 0.114309, 0.012584], [0.141569, 0.195631, 0.048916000000000015, 0.012584], [0.745873, 0.204646, 0.13644500000000004, 0.012584], [0.727152, 